Sentencas: A co-planar type single chamber solid oxide fuel cell (SC-SOFC) with linearly patterned electrode structures on the same surface as the electrolyte has been fabricated by robo-dispensing method.
Titulo: Co-planar type single chamber solid oxide fuel cell with micro-patterned electrodes

Sentencas: Paste materials of NiO-SDC-Pd cermet and (La0.7Sr0.3)(0.95)MnO3 (LSM) were selectively deposited onto a substrate of yttria stablized zirconia (YSZ) by extrusion through a syringe nozzle.
Titulo: Co-planar type single chamber solid oxide fuel cell with micro-patterned electrodes

Sentencas: The dispensed pastes were solidified upon solvent evaporation, and the anode and the cathode were sintered at 1350 degrees C for 2 h and 1200 degrees C for 1h, respectively.
Titulo: Co-planar type single chamber solid oxide fuel cell with micro-patterned electrodes

Sentencas: We have fabricated SC-SOFCs that have a single electrode pair with varying anode-to-cathode distances and interdigitated patterned electrodes with 2, 4, and 8 multiple pairs.
Titulo: Co-planar type single chamber solid oxide fuel cell with micro-patterned electrodes

Sentencas: The electrode microstructures of the resulting cells were examined by SEM.
Titulo: Co-planar type single chamber solid oxide fuel cell with micro-patterned electrodes

Sentencas: The electrochemical performance of the SC-SOFCs was also analyzed using impedance spectroscopy and a DC source meter.
Titulo: Co-planar type single chamber solid oxide fuel cell with micro-patterned electrodes
